-- BankUnited to Stay Independent After Review
-- B y   R i c k   G r e e n
-- 2012-01-18T22:46:11Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-18/bankunited-to-stay-independent-after-review.html
BankUnited Inc., the Florida lender
run by John Kanas, plans to stay independent instead of finding
a buyer.  “A preliminary process did occur whereby the company
considered its strategic alternatives,” the  Miami Lakes ,
Florida-based company said today in a statement. “That process
has concluded” and BankUnited will continue “as an independent
institution.”  To contact the reporter on this story:
Rick Green in New York at 
 rgreen18@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
